t something reliable and comfortable with bags of character then look no further than a used Mercedes S Class.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Audi_A8\"><\/span><b>Audi A8<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you&#x2019;re looking to own an Audi, but cannot afford one brand new, then it is time to look into buying a pre-owned model. The A8 from 2009 is one of the finest luxury sedans on offer and comes with the 4.2-liter V8 engine, Quattro all-wheel-drive system, and a 6-speed automatic transmission.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Land_Rover_Range_Rover_Sport\"><\/span><b>Land Rover Range Rover Sport<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you&#x2019;re looking to drive around in comfort, safety, and style on both Indian and foreign roads, it&#x2019;s hard to beat a Land Rover. While prices may vary depending on demand and other factors, it&#x2019;s possible to pick up a 2013 Range Rover Sport at below Rs 100 lakh. At that price, you get one of the most powerful engines among its competitors (the legendary 5.0L V8), as well as an extremely comfortable interior that can seat up to 7 people comfortably.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Jaguar_XJL_Supercharged\"><\/span><b>Jaguar XJL Supercharged<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This classic car is not only good-looking but also a perfect blend of speed and style. It has elegant interiors with intuitive design and premium comfort with front sporty seating arrangement and 7 seat option. In spite of its bigger size, it is faster than any other sports car in its segment due to a powerful V8 engine that delivers 542bhp. The auto variant gets an 8-speed transmission system with paddle-shift controls that helps you to accelerate faster. The car enjoys a top speed of 300 kmph.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Best_second_hand_luxury_car_under_5_lakhs\"><\/span><b>Best second hand luxury car under 5 lakhs<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Audi A4, Mercedes Benz C Class, and BMW 3 Series are some excellent second-hand options. If you&#x2019;re looking to buy a certified pre-owned luxury car then stick to models from brands like Mercedes and BMW, which have been producing new cars for decades and have kept their old models up to date with changes so that there is no compromise on safety or quality. When you buy a used car, it pays to know about maintenance, common issues, and parts so that you can check out cars carefully before making your purchase. Here are some important tips you should keep in mind when buying an old model<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Best-used_luxury_SUV_to_buy_in_India\"><\/span><b>Best-used luxury SUV to buy in India<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Range Rover has a legendarily luxurious interior and rich history, and as long as you don&#x2019;t need all that space on a daily basis, it&#x2019;s an affordable option. This particular model is available in Mumbai, Pune, Bangalore, and Kolkata.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Most_reliable_used_luxury_cars_in_India\"><\/span><b>Most reliable used luxury cars in India<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Buying a used car is never an easy task. There are many things to consider before buying a used car, such as quality, maintenance cost, and safety. If you&#x2019;re looking to buy a pre-owned Mercedes or BMW, you need to be extra careful.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cheapest_second-hand_luxury_cars_in_India\"><\/span><b>Cheapest second-hand luxury cars in India<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A good way to save money on a new car is to look at second-hand options. While some may find it unappealing to buy a used car, it&#x2019;s an incredibly economical option and can offer fantastic savings &#x2013; around 50 percent or more off new-car prices. There are many benefits to buying a used vehicle, including lower costs, a wider range of choices, and low maintenance costs once you have bought.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you&#x2019;re looking to buy a luxury car but don&#x2019;t want to pay the brand new price, you might be in luck. While used cars don&#x2019;t have the same appeal as their new counterparts,&#46;&#46;&#46;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":200024,"featured_media":2620,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2569"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/200024"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2569"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2569\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2618,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2569\/revisions\/2618"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2620"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2569"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category